      public java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> readDefaultValues​(java.lang.String dir, int x, int y)

      Parameters:
      dir - Directory of the text file
      x - The x coordinate of the entity
      y - The y coordinate of the entity
      Returns:
      Each item in the list is a line to be outputted in level.txt
